org.nasdanika.engineering

Interface Engineer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Adaptable, EngineeredElement, EObject, Forum, Marked, ModelElement, NamedElement, Notifier, Period, Persona
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Organization
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EngineerImpl, OrganizationImpl

    public interface Engineer
extends Persona
    A representation of the model object 'Engineer'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Modules
    • Owns
    • Expertise
    • Increments
    • Services
    • Personas
    • Assignments
    • Issue Categories
    • Issue Statuses
    • Issue Priorities
    • Issue Severities
    • Rate
    • Designations
    • Capacity
    • Represents
    • Messages
    • Objectives
    • Domains
    See Also:
    EngineeringPackage.getEngineer()

      • getDesignations

        EList<Allocation> getDesignations()
        Returns the value of the 'Designations' reference list. The list contents are of type Allocation. It is bidirectional and its opposite is 'Engineer'. Allocations of this [engineer](Engineer.html)'s [capacity](Capacity.html) to work on an [engineered element](EngineeredElement.hml) [issues](Issue.html) for a particular [endeavor](Endeavor.html) and [issue category](IssueCategory.html).
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Designations' reference list.
        See Also:
        EngineeringPackage.getEngineer_Designations(), Allocation.getEngineer()
